      "para_id": "Q000983.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ningal , his lady , Amar-Suena , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , built the Ĝipar-kug , her beloved temple . He dedicated it to her for his well-being ."
    }
